{"tid":518003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[炸彈都係X] 手榴彈一米距離爆炸 大陸兵幾無恙站起來","createTime":"2018-01-03T00:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T00:59:22.000Z","uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"122033c18a40c59e6877386d5bf55fafe243211c","tid":518003,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:57:14.000Z","msg":"【手榴彈一米距離爆炸 官兵幾無恙站起來】<br />\n【新兵投彈蝦碌多面睇】<br />\n<br />\n內地新兵必考項目：投擲手榴彈到30米外，方可合格。少數新丁緊張得手心大量出汗，令手榴彈滑落身邊幾米之內，險象環生。<br />\n<br />\n與其說考新兵擲彈技巧，倒不如說考教官逃生反應，千鈞一發間捉住新兵跳落避險坑，逃過一劫。<br />\n<br />\n考試失意的軍人不時成為內地傳媒報道的焦點，甚至現身中央電視台，不過報道角度全都是敏捷的長官如何捨身保護士兵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/085703_043ab0ec0976b0963523d742dc22973c.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F085703_043ab0ec0976b0963523d742dc22973c.PNG&h=012991ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"863b3073148d71791c3647a2c9e5d0a9790e6430","tid":518003,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1601276033350210/?hc_ref=ARS0iDiefEelsQezqz7C5JWuQ7x-g8rsp0Idz9KswdioQJYNXOa42rqBlZH4a-uiWwI&amp;fref=nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1601276033350210%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DARS0iDiefEelsQezqz7C5JWuQ7x-g8rsp0Idz9KswdioQJYNXOa42rqBlZH4a-uiWwI%26fref%3Dnf&d=3OAKf2X8IJcTyEPzQ8wmjTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c82353ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1601276033350210/?hc_ref=ARS0iDiefEelsQezqz7C5JWuQ7x-g8rsp0Idz9KswdioQJYNXOa42rqBlZH4a-uiWwI&amp;fref=nf</a>"}]}